![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/dfa9efe8-ca93-4f1a-a273-810604c9f000/20240405_173637.jpg?format=original)

*   **_ANDRE THE GIANT_** **_BATTLE ROYALE_**
    

A fairly normal battle Royale. Nothing to write home about.

*   **_WINNER: BRONSON REED_**
    

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/37d23469-59b5-4882-b5fe-4fe603abd6c7/Screenshot_20240405_174517.jpg?format=original)

Logan Paul sent Austin Theory and Grayson Waller to the site of Wrestlemania XL, the Lincoln Financial Field, to find and jump Randy Orton and Kevin Owens, but they were under the ring.

They take out Logan Paul to close the segment

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/95f729d9-d4f1-4bc5-84b0-95a1ee4718c2/Screenshot_20240405_174534.jpg?format=original)

