![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/ceda1950-0566-4ce5-baec-848b3d560a63/20240405_174543.jpg?format=original)

Dragon Lee is found ambushed backstage

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/b1051404-273f-478d-9158-be38d3f273c3/20240405_175242.jpg?format=original)

*   **_ELECTRA LOPEZ vs ZELINA VEGA_**
    

Santos Escobar and his gang come out with Andrade on their side. This upsets Zelina Vega, his former manager and friend.

This match was ROUGH to watch.

*   **_WINNER: ELECTRA LOPEZ_**
    

A brawl breaks out post match.

**_ANDRADE REUNITES WITH ZELINA VEGA!!_**

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/992aaa99-fe41-4f81-916e-408285a54fee/20240405_175534.jpg?format=original)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/6de28df6-852f-4c4a-8422-543f9e5e2d31/20240405_180036.jpg?format=original)

**_Belair and Naomi came to the ring first and Belair began by saying she has been fighting Damage CTRL longer than anyone._**

**_Belair said then Naomi showed up and reminded Belair why she was fighting in the first place. Naomi noted how Belair was "getting dragged every week." Naomi then said they are going to WrestleMania, they pointed to the sign and everyone cheered._**

**_Belair said Damage CTRL's problem is that they've been at the top for so long, they weren't expecting anyone else to come through. Cue Cargill's entrance._**

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f752a042-84f5-4a41-973b-7beeba19379a/received_1607146256789618.jpeg?format=original)

**_Cargill began by thanking Belair and Naomi once she got in the ring. Cargill said Damage CTRL "stepped up and got stepped on" and now Cargill will get to show the WWE Universe what she is all about._**

**_Cargill said they will show why there's "no damage control." Cargill told Damage CTRL they are now "in the eye of the storm." Cargill's music then hit and the three women pointed at the WrestleMania sign to end things._**

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/bd96d0d7-9822-4a67-a9f6-b2dc9dffab55/20240405_181205.jpg?format=original)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/4e56a7c8-225a-40dd-a04d-8a7b88b5fc4c/20240405_181939.jpg?format=original)

Dragon Lee is unable to compete at WrestleMania, so Rey skips over Carlito and choses Andrade to team up instead.

Carlito is NOT happy. 👀

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/ff72955d-957c-451e-86c9-e63df7fdd096/20240405_185547.jpg?format=original)

*   **_New Catch Republic (Tyler Bate & Pete Dunne) vs Grayson Waller & Austin Theory_**
    

Decent match with both teams looking as well as they can under 8 minutes.

*   **_WINNERS: NEW CATCH REPUBLIC_**
    

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f86a09a9-78b4-497c-9f9d-c24c4ccc791c/Screenshot_20240405_185534.jpg?format=original)

**_Post-Match Judgment Day ran out and attacked both teams. This included Rhea Ripley, who watched as each member performed their finisher on members of both teams._** 

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/5ac476bd-1336-457e-8487-20000383df9a/Screenshot_20240405_190322.jpg?format=original)

*   **_LA KNIGHT/AJ STYLES PROMO_**
    

Video of last week's angle with AJ Styles aired. Knight stood in the ring and the crowd chanted his name.

Knight almost choked on his gum.

Knight gave the "Let me talk to ya" line and everyone erupted. Knight kept saying "Yeah!" and the crowd ate it up. Knight took off his sunglasses and said he thinks Styles is phenomenal - "at not showing up and running away." Knight stumbled and the crowd helped him along.

Knight told Styles to grab his crying towel because all Styles has been doing is crying about Knight. Knight said he makes Styles interesting and he's going to give Styles "three the hard way" as he boots him through the field goal posts. Knight closed with the "LA Knight, yeah!" catchphrase and that was it. No shenanigans.

* * *

Bobby Lashley's group cut a vignette promo. B-Fab said there will be nowhere for the Final Testament to hide. Lashley chimed in and said this weekend, they will finish the Final Testament. Jey Uso then made his entrance and the crowd was way, way, way into it.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/34e7669b-ad10-4cb6-9c76-f015872e29f1/20240405_185459.jpg?format=original)

*   **_JEY USO VS SOLO SIKOA_**
    

Pretty nothing match. About 6 minutes long.

*   **_WINNER: JEY USO_**
    

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/c6c130e5-8d22-4534-9b5b-e83aec963893/Screenshot_20240405_190202.jpg?format=original)

Smackdown closes with Jimmy Uso getting jumped by Jey, Cody and Seth before Cody tells the world he IS going to dethrone the Tribal Cheif.

